parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning wiper blades can obstruct the driver's view, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Wiper blades do not recline to the proper position
making a loud noise
obstructing the lower view of the windshield
and affecting the washer function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unintended stopping of the vehicle can cause accidents, injuries, or whiplash, especially when driving in reverse.
symptoms: The vehicle comes to a complete and sudden halt
making a loud crash sound
without any warning lights or sounds indicating an obstruction or pending crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Failure and Imminent Crash Warning System Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes and imminent crash warning system can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Brakes fail
car crashes
and the imminent crash warning system does not come on
and airbags do not deploy.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: High-Voltage Battery Warning and Hybrid Powertrain System Fault
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The high-voltage battery warning and hybrid powertrain system fault can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Warning messages appear
such as "high-voltage battery warning" and "The hybrid powertrain system has detected a fault"
and the vehicle may shut down or stall.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning door ajar notification can cause distractions, accidents, or injuries, especially at night.
symptoms: The door ajar notification continues to illuminate when all doors are secure
causing dome lights to continue to illuminate
and preventing doors from locking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the back-over prevention camera system can increase the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when reversing, as the driver may not be aware of obstacles or pedestrians behind the vehicle.
symptoms: The back-over prevention camera screen turns blue
the camera screen goes dark
the camera does not detect obstacles or pedestrians
the warning alert is delayed or does not sound
the system glitches or malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Roof leaks can cause water damage to the interior, rust, and electrical issues, which can lead to safety risks and compromise the vehicle's overall performance.
symptoms: Unusual sound of water running from the roof
moldy odor coming through the air vents
visible water stains on the roof liner
rust stains on the liner.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The hood latch failure can cause the hood to pop open while driving, obstructing the driver's view and potentially leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The hood pops open while driving
especially when hitting a bump
the hood stops at the first catch
the hood can be relatched successfully.
